{"tid":530442,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"The Cranberries主唱倫敦過世　死因未明","createTime":"2018-01-15T18:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T15:57:58.000Z","uid":54081,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"dfec78c04d17963f2ae39210a31ce94f6660c642","tid":530442,"uid":54081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T18:24:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180116/1279257/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180116%2F1279257%2F&d=WyiZAUpg5RWpngKUq%2FFX%2B49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=aebd7da3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180116%2F1279257%2F&h=0a21bceb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180116/1279257/</a><br />\n1990年代紅遍全球的愛爾蘭另類搖滾樂團「小紅莓」(The Cranberries)主唱歐里歐丹(Dolores O'Riordan)，周一(15日)傳出在英國倫敦「突然過世」，享年46歲，歐里歐丹的發言人證實了這個消息。<br />\n《鏡報》報導，來自愛爾蘭的天才女歌手歐里歐丹，是在倫敦進行一場「短暫的錄音」時意外過世的，目前死因尚未證實。<br />\n「小紅莓」樂團的另類搖滾曲風，在1990年代初期引領風騷，從歐陸紅遍全球，知名單曲如《Dream》曾被天后王菲翻唱為《夢中人》，2005年後歐里歐丹推出數張個人專輯，「小紅莓」樂團也在2009年重組。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c211f9b7cfbd93c470bc9f38b4f027459ec07fe","tid":530442,"uid":54081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T18:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.g